tip_battle.message: You can't attack Norg until you take out the Norg Pod first, kupo! The Left Orb and Right Orb on either side change from blue, to yellow, and then red. If an orb makes it to red, it will unleash a powerful magic attack, but you can send an orb back to the previous color by attacking it, so target the orbs to keep them in check!
tip_battle.title: Norg

tip_battle.message: Granaldo and the Raldos have their very own Combo Attack, so take down one or the other first to keep them from using it!
tip_battle.title: Granaldo

sp_scores.title: Defeat the Archaeosaur without being KO'd.

tip_battle.message: Archaeosaur uses the devastating group attack Tail Lash, but you can lash back with debuffs, kupo! Use Sleep, Paralyze, and Blind to keep the odds in your favor!

tip_battle.message: Oilboyle counters attacks with Oil Blast, kupo, and that means you'll end up Blinded or Sapped! Tip the odds back in your favor by exploiting its weakness, fire!
